{"tid":595462,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"出黎做野先發現自己冇乜朋友","createTime":"2018-03-16T16:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T15:04:59.000Z","uid":6425,"like":132,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"88c94da004328f541b0c8b0ab5be37f30347c9dd","tid":595462,"uid":6425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T16:05:04.000Z","msg":"本身中學keep到聯絡既得番幾個，唔會成日約出黎又唔會日日傾計咁<br />\n可能大家做野忙，冇得成日見，圈子又唔同左<br />\n大學friend近乎係冇，入左U以為玩ocamp上莊住hall可以識到好多friend<br />\n但識到都keep唔到，頂多hi bye，出黎做野更加冇聯絡<br />\n同好多曾經既朋友都疏遠晒<br />\n例如莊期果時好熟，但大家畢晒業又冇乜聯絡<br />\n依加番工識果啲同事，又唔覺得大家熟到變朋友，加上職場野又複雜<br />\n出去參加咩活動都唔會主動認識新朋友<br />\n<br />\n其實自己都知咩事 <br />\n例如毒啦，唔主動識人呀去維繫呀<br />\n講野唔多，俾人感覺好串好cool<br />\n又唔會話好需要人地陪<br />\n唔太鍾意出去玩<br />\n同其他人冇咩共同興趣同topic<br />\n<br />\n覺得自己唔特別用心去維繫啲關係係因為自己唔太care<br />\n不過有時都覺得幾唏噓<br />\n唔知有冇人明果種矛盾"},{"pid":"7ae1fff639cf45fb99bb3616ee24d7bbff8afdea","tid":595462,"uid":7957,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T16:08:24.000Z","msg":"習慣到自己一個<br />\n就會覺得朋友係可有可無"},{"pid":"13d1c68be5256ab28cf6227928698b6f0fa30c28","tid":595462,"uid":45772,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T16:22:56.000Z","msg":"有上莊住hall都可以冇朋友&hellip;？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71314042b952fd0744e61aea17cdcd71a9b22812","tid":595462,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T16:23:22.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"07d74f534d2971e7cbb8e20a592251dc7bf65b95","tid":595462,"uid":123308,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"quote":{"pid":"13d1c68be5256ab28cf6227928698b6f0fa30c28","tid":595462,"uid":45772,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T16:22:56.000Z","msg":"有上莊住hall都可以冇朋友&hellip;？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /